週次 Week進度說明 Progress Description
1有「國籍」意義的名詞。用名詞工具格來表示時間。 1.	Citizenship and ethnicity nouns. Instrumental to express time.2「學習」的動詞。詢問。建議。拒絕。同意。感謝。‘Study’ verbs. Interrogation. Proposal. Objection. Gratitude.3表示日期。[s] (跟）介詞與工具格名詞。 Expression of dates. C (with) preposition and instrumental.4裝飾詞工具格。有些動詞。有些介詞。建議。定時間。評價。 Adjective instrumental. Verbs and prepositions. Suggestion. Setting timing. Evaluation.5多方向動作動詞。附合主語。不肯定代名詞。「假設」結構。Multidirectional verbs. Subject opposition. Indefinite pronouns. Constructions with subjunctive.6表示時間（半小時）。「sam」代名詞。請求幫忙。建議幫助。詢問。敘述。指示。 Time (‘half an hour’). Reflexive pronoun ‘sam’. Asking for help. Extending help. Interrogation. Narration. Direction.7「視聽」類動詞的結構。名詞與形容詞複數介詞格。工具格其他應用。 Perception verbs. Noun and adjective prepositional plural. Other uses of instrumental.8表達不確定。表示可能性。請求。禮貌談話。正式談話。 Expression of uncertainty. Expression of possibility. Asking for something. Polite talk. Official talk.9索短的句子。主語和謂語的關係。有些動詞的變化。 Elliptic constructions. Subject-predicate relations. Some particular verbs.10期中考試。 Mid-term exam.11數字變格。複數工具格。俄羅斯之姓變格。詢問。敘述。 Declension of numerals. Instrumental plural. Surnames declension. Interrogation, narration.12特殊形容詞。無生命所有者的結構。間接命令。 Special adjectives. Impersonal possessor. Indirect command. 13裝飾詞複數生格。自我介紹。學習談話。 Adjective genitive plural. Self-introducing. Talk on studies.14動詞後的工具格。名詞、裝飾詞複數予格。 Instrumental after some verbs. Accusative plural of nouns and adjectives.15形容詞和副詞比較程度。詢問。敘述。建議。 Comparative degree of adjectives and adverbs. Interrogation, narration, proposition.16被動式行動詞。複數名詞變格。 Passive mood verbs. Noun plural declension.17常用的後綴。詢問。敘述。  行動詞。狀動詞。 Some common suffixes. Interrogation, narration. Participle. Adverbial participle.
18期末考試 Final exam 

